snippet.title: Judgment | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Judgment is headed to the West on June 25, 2019! Digital pre-orders get early access to the full game starting on June 21. 

https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0177-CUSA13186_00-JUDGMENTRYUGAENG

A star-studded English voice cast brings Judgment to life. Greg Chun takes on the role of Judgment’s protagonist, Takayuki Yagami, supported by Crispin Freeman, Matthew Mercer, Cherami Leigh, Yuri Lowenthal, James Hong, Ed O’Ross, Amy Walker, Matt Yang King, Fred Tatasciore, Brian McNamara, as well as guest appearances by SungWon Cho, Cristina Vee, Max Mittelman, and many more.

For the latest updates:

Web: http://sega.vg/DyNo30mUiH6
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RGGStudio
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RGGStudioWest/
